result.name: monthly_figures_on_children_entering_detention
result.notes:
Monthly statistics relating to children entering detention and held solely under Immigration Act powers.  These data are based on provisional management information and are subject to change.

Source agency: Home Office

Designation: Official Statistics not designated as National Statistics

Language: English

Alternative title: Monthly figures on children entering detention

organization.name: home-office
organization.title: Home Office
organization.description:
The Home Office leads on immigration and passports, drugs policy, crime policy and counter-terrorism and works to ensure visible, responsive and accountable policing in the UK.

Home Office is a ministerial department, supported by 26 agencies and public bodies.

https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office
